{"id":201901,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/维权网-妙觉法师、田喜母亲等探访艾未未遭拦截-2/","date":"2011-12-05T09:01:04Z","modified":"2011-12-05T09:01:04Z","title":"维权网 &#124; 妙觉法师、田喜母亲等探访艾未未遭拦截被押至久敬庄（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a>（维权网信息员张兵报道）今日（2011年12月4日星期日）早上十点，妙觉法师、田喜母亲、网友无题及母亲等一起去探访艾未未家&#8212;&#8212;草场地258号。刚到草场地，妙觉法师给田妈妈照相，无题在敲未未的门，警察就来了。警察此时如临大敌。艾未未开门，让妙觉法师、田喜母亲等进去；但是警察挡住她们，不让她们进去并让艾未未关门。警察并且横过来拦住她们的去路，将她们抓了起来。 </p>\n<p>随后，警察把她们押到一辆朝阳区公安的车上，车是北京朝阳区南皋派出所的公安车辆，车牌是A6954 。开车送她们到久敬庄的是南皋派出所警察。妙觉法师、田喜妈妈、无题、无被抓到到了久敬庄后，她们看到久敬庄里的停着一长排警车，被困在久敬庄访民们很多。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qoLjApYGzog/TtsKrzhhe-I/AAAAAAAADR8/wB-LhD0avZs/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209px\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qoLjApYGzog/TtsKrzhhe-I/AAAAAAAADR8/wB-LhD0avZs/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320px\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3_Q0XxVAs_U/TtsKthIRw-I/AAAAAAAADSE/NlTfkthMHsk/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209px\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3_Q0XxVAs_U/TtsKthIRw-I/AAAAAAAADSE/NlTfkthMHsk/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320px\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kN4Qyxu1-yI/TtsKvgL2ZuI/AAAAAAAADSM/-dBgNsi7Vt4/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"218px\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kN4Qyxu1-yI/TtsKvgL2ZuI/AAAAAAAADSM/-dBgNsi7Vt4/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320px\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7936444186405756379?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> </p>\n<p>\n</form>\n","author":1001,"categories":[1],"tags":[8906,9484]}